{"tid":1568991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日大家唔好再重蹈覆轍","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:28:48.000Z","uid":13189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9dd637adad9fb21e29ace95c1bdd5435c9d08d","tid":1568991,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"831個日啲狗已經打死左我地3個手足，我希望前線真係做到hit and run，唔好留戀對峙啦，陣地戰無贏面嫁，玩魔法就唔好圍爐 要趁機會退啦。831太子站大家都知點解會搞成咁，離場個陣見到啲搞事撚一係就私了，一係就唔撚理佢，唔好比佢地引到大家企定定係到屌佢呀，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HIT AND RUN</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HIT AND RUN</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HIT AND RUN</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">915, 維園見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5fReug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5fReug.jpg&h=3a9b3e79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cd99e5baa1e2b7d529a64a8e5962e4b98f16479","tid":1568991,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=7491afc5\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"3b9f484b5cc381034db14fa36fecd5e085cd8edf","tid":1568991,"uid":117906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea36569449ca2dac1bba913a79270b51ccfe4632","tid":1568991,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"761524e94e5a99d4c05667c9da9595ea39b79eae","tid":1568991,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"915 維園 東角"},{"pid":"726299771c6026978ec21cf68d5c5ac5587004c8","tid":1568991,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:02:51.000Z","msg":"主動出擊，hit and run!"},{"pid":"42e665034a498287ae3091e3764b3c028a27bcf4","tid":1568991,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"